title: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map
description: Description: An exception is thrown when exporting data from the attached report.
SR: Bug 121682: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table containing highlight/map. Follow these steps: 1. Add a table that has a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row. 2. Preview the attached report. 3. Export the data from the table.
